text t5 "is it vibecoded?\n- yes!\n\nis it useful?\n- absolutely!\n\nshould it be a foundational piece\nin any serious production pipeline?\n-absolutely not\n\nif its vibecoded, doesnt that mean I can re-build this?\n- absolutely, but maybe we can improve it together?\n\nis it ironic to vibe-code a tool with a proprietary LLM model that is\nonly good because of large scale theft and then open source the tool?\n- yeah" -61.75 573.6214225570593
text t6 "I'd argue when an output is easy to judge (flowgo file, visual map) the amount of\nhuman judgement we can apply to the HOW of the output can decrease\ngiven basic ethics and security is in place" -299.2240395885792 1069.4856902282372 7 5
